metadata.name: Mobius Key #1/13
metadata.description:
The Mobius Keys grant access to 🐋🏴‍☠️🐋, Thee Mobius Royale', a pirate hideaway tucked into the digital realm of Spatial.io metaverse.

- These keys are the entry point on your way to becoming a pirate in the crew of 🏴‍☠️🕸🕸🕸🏴‍☠️.eth

- The King Keys will allow one to purchase a King Prince Pirate ENS subdomain in the future as part of your pirate identity.  
(Ex: black💎.🏴‍☠️🤴🏿🏴‍☠️.eth)

 - Choose from the 5 variations  
🏴‍☠️🤴🏿🏴‍☠️.eth  
🏴‍☠️🤴🏾🏴‍☠️.eth  
🏴‍☠️🤴🏽🏴‍☠️.eth  
🏴‍☠️🤴🏼🏴‍☠️.eth  
🏴‍☠️🤴🏻🏴‍☠️.eth

- Keys will be released in batches of 25-50/monthly until set of 321 is reached for bot h Kings/Queens.

- Half will be Kings/ Half will be Queens every month w/ crowned skull jewel coinciding w/ birth stone of that month.

- Thee 💎God💎 suggests you choose your key accordingly for it will be the basis of your pirate & access points.
